The subject deals with principles and methods of learning and teaching used in primary school. It introduces primary school lesson planning and preparation according to the national curriculum of basic school. Primary school lessons are observed and analysed based on video material.Objectives/eesmärkid:  General aim is to provide the students with an overview of principles of learning and teaching in primary schooland activities connected with teaching.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  The student having completed the subject: 1)  knows the curriculum of primary school; 2) knows the methods of learning and teaching in primary school and can apply them when teaching different subjects; 3) notices similarities and differences between primary school and kindergarten study activities.
